These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, drawing, gardening, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, sports, musical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, handball, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, scooter, bus
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##8
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 3. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 8. the person watching musical movies is between the person driving the subway and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
 9. the person driving the bus is the person watching sports movies##1
10. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
13. the person watching sports movies is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
14. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person driving the scooter##1
15. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | writing     | drawing   | skydiving | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | musical   | disaster   | sports  |
| Sport         | skateboarding  | handball  | swimming  | rowing |
| Transport     | quad-bike    | scooter | subway     | bus    |

