.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, 7up, coffee
There 4 different types of food: potato, cucumber, mango, nectarine
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, folk, classical, reggae
4 different pets are kept: horse, goat, hedgehog, chinchilla
 1. the fan of classical is between the owner of the horse and the fan of folk##2
 2. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
 5. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
 6. the person eating nectarine is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of country is the owner of the goat##1
10. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
11. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the fan of classical##8
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the person eating cucumber##5
14. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
15. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating potato##1
17. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
18. the person eating cucumber is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
19. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up | coffee  | fanta  |
| Food          | nectarine     | cucumber | potato | mango  |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | classical  | reggae | country |
| Pet           | hedgehog | chinchilla | horse    | goat  |

