 2. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the fan of metal##5
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the left of the person watching horror movies##8
 7. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
