The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, photographer, lawyer, freelancer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, ice-hockey, water-polo
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the entrepreneur##6
 2. the freelancer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 3. the person eating radish is the lawyer##1
 4. the person eating grapes is between the entrepreneur and the photographer##2
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 6. the person who's sport is handball is not to the right of the person eating grapes##8
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the freelancer##1
10. the photographer is the person who's sport is handball##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person eating onion##8
12. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
14. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
15. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
