 2. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the entrepreneur##8
 3. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 4. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 5. the person driving the car is the colombian##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the malaysian##8
 7. the person drinking juice is not the australian##6
 8. the lawyer is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person drinking juice##7
 9. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
11. the dancer is on the right of the firefighter##1
12. the lawyer is not the american##6
13. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
14. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the lawyer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
