 4. the scientist is the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking lemonade##7
 7. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
 8. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
 9. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
10. the pilot is not to the left of the pilot##8
11. the manager is on the far left##1
12. the fisherman is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is photography##1
14. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
15. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
16. the pilot is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8

.:: Answer ::.
