 3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8
 9. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
11. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite   | tea     | soy-milk    | milk |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | electronic      | salsa     | metal     |
| Sport         | swimming | basketball  | cricket     | sailing  |
| Transport     | skateboard     | scooter | car | jet-ski     |

